{"tid":1231981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人會想將遊行同示威變成生活嘅習慣","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T14:48:26.000Z","uid":199893,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfa7a69b7c9b5f730d8ee9654c5b77705087fbf","tid":1231981,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到自己69 612 616都有出港島<br />\n你問我攰唔攰，我實話攰架<br />\n你問香港人攰唔攰，香港人實話攰架<br />\n但係，政府一日唔回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n我地仍然會一直上街抗爭<br />\n爭取返屬於我地嘅自己同權利<br />\n<br />\n如果可以安穩，冇人會想動盪<br />\n如果可以安穩，冇人會想摒棄休息而拖住疲倦嘅身軀上街<br />\n如果可以安穩......<br />\n好多好多嘢都會唔同<br />\n<br />\n但係，係你迫鳩我地出嚟反你架，林鄭月娥<br />\n你真係以為我地好得閒好有興致嚟經常上街反你？<br />\n你真係以為香港人好鍾意隔兩三日就出嚟屌你老母一次？<br />\n<br />\n我想講，冇人會希望、會鍾意將遊行同示威變成自己生活嘅常態同習慣<br />\n我相信一班香港人已經好攰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係，應該要做嘅，我地仍會去做</span><br />\n<br />\n今日616，有多過200萬人上街遊行，我唔係想講得咩嘢<br />\n我只係想講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你惹唔起香港人架，林鄭月娥</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後我想幫呢位巴打推一推我地嘅訴求，跪求大家一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［推上報］要求政府午夜前撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1231386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1231386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60e1a4f187086fed9d5895768754d30d5dc334ba","tid":1231981,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"